Merge pull request #28 from Ewg777/patch-1

Update HVCoreDataHandler.m

Update HVCoreDataHandler.m

Crash fix when trying to pass UIImage

Merge pull request #23 from dfens/master

Get rid of ugly whitespace
Removed links to deprecated GitHub downloads section.

Update README.md

added '+ add QuartzCore to frameworks list' step
Pretty example has model ( Core Data )

Update README.md

+ instructions for Core Data Viewer

tweaks before release for core data viewer
data for first watched context is shown automatically
changes UI Viewer html file name ( "index2" was strange )

refactor at HVCoreDataHandler
improved Core Data viewer look&feel

fixed warrnings
basic UI for Core Data viewer
fixed compilation error at PrettyExample project

- static resources ( html/css/js ) are exported to C-like header files as define directive
Example:
index.html -> #define INDEX @"[base64 of index.html]"
- static resources header files are generated by XCODE's script
- added API for getting NSManagedObjectContext scheme
- added API for fetching the data from NSManagedObjectContext
fixed bug when application didn;t allow to view custom windows properties

Merge pull request #6 from forresty/fix-cocoapods

fix 1.4 CocoaPods error by moving defs to HVDefines.h

Fixed rendering when view.transform ( or view.layer.transform ) different than identity
Properties column displays view.layer properties under "CALayer" group

added release.py script
(it builds fat library, checks local version number with the latest one from github, compress build results to .zip file)
update base64 version of index file
Views tree expands to selected UI element when user click UI element at preview
web app display version of iOS Hierarchy Viewer

fixed crashes at UITextView:
+ some properties can be read only from UI thread
+ some properties ( like 'autocapitalizationType' ) are not KVC compliant.
